# Configuration Files

Key project configuration files:

- `[package.json](mdc:package.json)`: Manages project dependencies and scripts.
- `[tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)`: Configures the TypeScript compiler options.
- `[next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js)`: Configures Next.js specific settings.
- `[tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts)`: Configures Tailwind CSS utility classes and theme.
- `[components.json](mdc:components.json)`: Likely related to shadcn/ui component configuration.
- `[.eslintrc.json](mdc:.eslintrc.json)`: Configures ESLint for code linting.
- `[.gitignore](mdc:.gitignore)`: Specifies intentionally untracked files that Git should ignore.
- `[postcss.config.mjs](mdc:postcss.config.mjs)`: Configuration for PostCSS processing.
